        public UserSwitchResult(int status,
                        java.lang.Integer androidFailureStatus,
                        java.lang.String errorMessage)
        Creates a new UserSwitchResult.
        参数:
        status - Gets the user switch result status.
        androidFailureStatus - Gets the failure status returned by UserManager when the status is STATUS_ANDROID_FAILURE.
        errorMessage - Gets the error message, if any.

      • getStatus

        public int getStatus()
        Gets the user switch result status.
        返回:
        either STATUS_SUCCESSFUL, STATUS_ANDROID_FAILURE, STATUS_HAL_FAILURE, STATUS_HAL_INTERNAL_FAILURE, STATUS_INVALID_REQUEST, STATUS_UX_RESTRICTION_FAILURE, STATUS_OK_USER_ALREADY_IN_FOREGROUND, STATUS_TARGET_USER_ALREADY_BEING_SWITCHED_TO, STATUS_TARGET_USER_ABANDONED_DUE_TO_A_NEW_REQUEST, STATUS_NOT_SWITCHABLE, or STATUS_NOT_LOGGED_IN.

      • getAndroidFailureStatus

        public java.lang.Integer getAndroidFailureStatus()
        Gets the failure status returned by UserManager when the status is STATUS_ANDROID_FAILURE.
        返回:
        USER_OPERATION_ERROR_ constants defined by UserManager, or null when the status is not STATUS_ANDROID_FAILURE.
